OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,FOnly a fifth of England fans are
OL,8,Fbacking the Three Lions to win the
OL,9,FFifa World Cup despite being among the
OL,10,Ffavourites to win, trailing behind
OL,11,Frivals when it comes to patriotic
OL,12,Fpunting, according to bookies.
OL,14,FBetting data from Ladbrokes and Coral
OL,15,Fowner Entain sheds light on how
OL,16,Fstrongly people are backing their home
OL,17,Fnations, ahead of the men's football
OL,18,Ftournament kicking off on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
