OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780880588
OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,FPortugal has the most loyal betters
OL,8,Fwith 57% of domestic slips placed on
OL,9,Fthe team.
OL,11,FThis is well above the second-most
OL,12,Fpatriotic country, France, with 29% of
OL,13,Fbets backing the team in the home
OL,14,Fmarket, followed by Austria at 25% and
OL,15,FGermany at 24%.
OL,17,FIn Britain, England trails behind with
OL,18,F20% home backing, but Scots are even
OL,19,Fless optimistic of lifting the World
OL,20,FCup trophy this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
