OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780880588
OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,FSome 9% of all bets placed in Scotland
OL,8,Fare backing the team, with the odds of
OL,9,Fthem winning at 300/1.
OL,11,FThe data from Entain covers bets
OL,12,Fplaced up to and including June 3,
OL,13,Fwith figures relating to the
OL,14,Fpercentage of slips and stakes placed
OL,15,Fby betters in each market on their
OL,16,Frespective home nation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
