OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780880588
OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,FThe betting stakes from Entain's
OL,8,Fglobal markets shows Spain in the lead
OL,9,Fas the most-backed team overall,
OL,10,Ffollowed by France, while England and
OL,11,FPortugal are level at third.
OL,13,FDespite confidence among rival
OL,14,Fcountries, Spanish punters are less
OL,15,Fpatriotic with 16% of bets placed
OL,16,Fbacking the home nation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
