CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780880588
OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,FThe data also revealed that there is
OL,8,Flimited cross-border support with 8%
OL,9,Fof Scots putting money on England to
OL,10,Fwin, and just 1% of English betters
OL,11,Fbacking Scotland to lift the trophy.
OL,13,FTom Ritzema, group trading director at
OL,14,FEntain, said the stakes show that
OL,15,F"football loyalty and betting logic
OL,16,Fdon't always go hand in hand".
OL,18,F"England fans are passionate, but
OL,19,Fyears of near misses have made them
OL,20,Fthink beyond their own country," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
