OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780880588
OL,3,CEngland fans less patriotic than
OL,4,Crivals on World Cup win, betting
OL,5,Cstakes show
OL,7,F"Portugal clearly stands out as the
OL,8,Fmost patriotic market, with fans
OL,9,Ffirmly backing their team, while
OL,10,Fcountries like France and Germany also
OL,11,Fshow strong belief.
OL,13,F"What's striking, though, is in the
OL,14,Fglobal picture Spain remains the most
OL,15,Fpopular choice across our markets,
OL,16,Fshowing that when it comes to this
OL,17,FWorld Cup, neutrals and patriots alike
OL,18,Fare looking beyond national borders
OL,19,Ffor their winner."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@RO]
